name: python-munin
body:
## Plugins

* AWS ELB
* AWS SQS
* Cassandra
* DD-WRT Wireless Rate & Signal
* Gearman
* Hookbox
* Memcached
* MongoDB
* MySQL
* Nginx
* PGBouncer
* Postgres
* RabbitMQ
* Redis
* Riak
* System
* Tokyo Cabinet
